# Extracted from: //www.rabbitmq.com/install-debian.html

Instalacion en Debian/Ubuntu:

	apt-get install rabbitmq-server (queue manager)
	pip3 install pika (rpc client and server)

System overview:
	RPC client (C)
	RPC server (S)
	Message queues: 
		RPC request: rpc-queue	
		RPC reply (implicit)

   rpc-request
 C ------>||||||req3|req2|req1|	-----> S for each req:
		rpc-queue			gets req
   rpc-reply				 	invoques func and obtaines response res
   <----- |res1|res2|res3||||||  <-----	 	send response res
		replies

RPC client:
	python3 client.py <fibonacci-num>

RPC server:
	python3 server.py 

Example: 
	   python3 server.py
	   python3 client.py 2 25 
